{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_13","type":"agent_message","text":"The failure is not a direct `Missing*RegistrationError`. Native image builds, but runtime blows up in Netty’s static initialization because `ResourceLeakDetector.addExclusions(...)` cannot find `toLeakAwareBuffer` on `io.netty.buffer.AbstractByteBufAllocator`. I’m tracing how other Netty modules model this kind of reflection so I can place the fix in the right metadata file without widening it unnecessarily."}}
